WEBVTT

00:00.800 --> 00:02.302
I've been waiting for you.
Oh...

00:02.769 --> 00:05.038
You're gonna need a lot more
than some lemons

00:05.038 --> 00:06.406
to cover that up.

00:06.406 --> 00:08.475
[Fatima]<i> Previously on</i> Sistas<i> .</i>

00:08.742 --> 00:11.144
That desk pisses me off.

00:11.144 --> 00:12.746
All these pictures of y'all...

00:12.746 --> 00:14.881
[music]

00:14.881 --> 00:16.750
Did you know they were engaged?

00:17.050 --> 00:18.084
Yes.

00:18.084 --> 00:19.586
You knew this the whole time?!

00:20.120 --> 00:21.121
What the?!

00:21.121 --> 00:23.089
She askin' for $500,000?!

00:23.089 --> 00:24.758
Where the -- she get
that number from?!

00:24.758 --> 00:25.892
I want you...

00:26.226 --> 00:27.727
...to marry me.

00:27.727 --> 00:28.728
[music]

00:32.658 --> 00:34.193
What the hell?

00:36.795 --> 00:38.197
Get, get up.

00:38.897 --> 00:39.832
No.

00:40.232 --> 00:42.301
I wanna marry you.

00:42.301 --> 00:44.470
You don't wanna marry me.

00:45.871 --> 00:47.106
Why would you say that?

00:47.106 --> 00:49.141
Because we're goin' through
all of this.

00:49.141 --> 00:52.144
Danni, we're just figurin'
each other out, is all.

00:52.144 --> 00:54.113
And that's why we shouldn't.

00:54.113 --> 00:58.584
[music]

00:58.584 --> 01:00.085
I'm serious.

01:01.487 --> 01:02.755
Get up.

01:02.755 --> 01:04.356
Not until you say yes.

01:04.356 --> 01:06.759
Okay.
Well, you gon' be down there.

01:06.759 --> 01:08.827
All day and all night.

01:08.827 --> 01:10.429
-Danni...
-I'm goin' to bed.

01:13.665 --> 01:16.101
Preston, that ring is for
another woman.

01:16.101 --> 01:17.403
I don't want it.

01:17.703 --> 01:18.670
Put it on.

01:19.104 --> 01:20.005
No.

01:20.873 --> 01:24.109
Just put it on, and you'll see
that it's your size.

01:24.643 --> 01:26.412
We might have
the same ring size!

01:26.412 --> 01:28.447
-That doesn't mean anything!
-[Preston] You don't.

01:28.447 --> 01:29.581
You don't.

01:29.581 --> 01:31.583
Preston, mm-mm.

01:34.787 --> 01:36.088
Danni...

01:36.722 --> 01:37.756
Do you love me?

01:38.557 --> 01:40.726
-[Danni] I think this is...
-You love me.

01:41.660 --> 01:42.728
You do.

01:42.728 --> 01:45.898
[music]

01:45.898 --> 01:46.832
Yes.

01:47.666 --> 01:48.967
Yes, I do.

01:48.967 --> 01:51.737
Okay...
So then, what's the problem?

01:51.937 --> 01:53.439
All of this.

01:55.374 --> 01:57.109
Shit, Dan...
Danni...

01:57.476 --> 01:59.278
I don't know what else to do.

02:00.379 --> 02:02.281
What, what do,
what do you mean?

02:02.281 --> 02:05.284
I mean, you wanna date me.

02:05.818 --> 02:07.352
Then you don't wanna date me.

02:08.053 --> 02:09.488
You wanna see me...

02:09.488 --> 02:12.224
and then you don't
wanna see me.

02:12.591 --> 02:15.694
So your solution is to ask me
to marry you?

02:17.129 --> 02:18.430
Danni...

02:19.398 --> 02:23.168
I'm willin' to do anything
for you.

02:25.504 --> 02:27.172
Thank you.

02:30.142 --> 02:31.777
What?

02:31.777 --> 02:33.212
But no.

02:33.212 --> 02:40.085
[music]

02:40.085 --> 02:41.487
I'm sorry.

02:42.221 --> 02:43.789
You're really sayin' no?

02:46.825 --> 02:47.826
I did.

02:48.794 --> 02:49.895
And I mean it.

02:49.895 --> 02:50.896
[music]

02:54.958 --> 02:56.894
<i>♪ My girls hold me down ♪</i>

02:56.894 --> 02:58.896
<i>♪ When them boys mess around ♪</i>

02:58.896 --> 03:00.998
<i>♪ My love life is a headache ♪</i>

03:00.998 --> 03:03.500
<i>♪ We goin' out tonight ♪</i>

03:03.500 --> 03:06.203
<i>♪ 'Cause I'm lookin' for love ♪</i>

03:10.032 --> 03:11.467
So you don't wanna marry me?

03:11.467 --> 03:13.035
You can't be serious right now,

03:13.035 --> 03:14.904
with all this that
we're goin' through.

03:14.904 --> 03:16.205
All of what, Danni?

03:16.205 --> 03:17.740
I'm not goin' through anything.

03:18.908 --> 03:20.443
Well, I guess I am.

03:20.977 --> 03:22.779
So...
You know.

03:23.146 --> 03:24.280
Okay...

03:24.514 --> 03:26.749
-Fine.
-[Danni] I'm sorry.

03:26.749 --> 03:28.985
[music]

03:28.985 --> 03:30.419
So you want me to marry her?

03:33.990 --> 03:36.159
That's what you heard.
Okay.

03:36.159 --> 03:38.728
Why...Why do you have
to be married right now,

03:38.728 --> 03:39.662
to either me or her?

03:39.662 --> 03:42.131
I'm just...
I'm tired of this.

03:42.131 --> 03:43.166
Mm-hm.

03:43.933 --> 03:46.536
[Preston] All the back and
forth, the theatrics of it all.

03:46.536 --> 03:48.304
Danni, I just wanna be with you.

03:48.304 --> 03:50.306
And I want you to be mine.

03:51.040 --> 03:52.408
That's all.

03:53.142 --> 03:55.711
You wanna be with me?
Okay, well...

03:55.711 --> 03:58.781
Piece of paper won't make
me yours, so...

03:59.782 --> 04:00.750
Then what will?

04:02.151 --> 04:03.119
My heart?

04:03.452 --> 04:06.622
It is not in this.
Whatever this is.

04:07.790 --> 04:08.724
[Preston] Okay.

04:11.694 --> 04:12.628
I'm sorry.

04:13.796 --> 04:16.265
Yeah.
Fine.

04:17.700 --> 04:19.068
I'mma go take a bath.

04:19.068 --> 04:23.439
[footsteps]

04:23.439 --> 04:25.842
You know, you are really
stressin' me out.

04:28.177 --> 04:30.079
Well, sorry about that.

04:30.079 --> 04:32.048
So I'mma just...

04:32.048 --> 04:34.350
chill out in the bathtub.
Okay?

04:35.751 --> 04:36.786
You want me to leave.

04:37.520 --> 04:39.388
Yep, Preston,
that's what I said.

04:39.388 --> 04:41.390
I said leave, because
I'm gon' go take a bath.

04:41.390 --> 04:42.925
[Preston] I'm asking.

04:42.925 --> 04:45.761
You can watch TV, you can chill.
I just want you to relax, bro.

04:45.761 --> 04:49.932
Relax.
Just don't overthink it, okay?

04:49.932 --> 04:51.267
Oh, shit.

04:51.267 --> 04:53.536
What, what, what now?

04:53.536 --> 04:54.570
Hm?

04:55.204 --> 04:56.672
I shoulda waited.

04:56.672 --> 04:57.773
Yeah.

04:58.241 --> 05:00.009
Two or three years
would be nice.

05:00.009 --> 05:01.644
[Preston] No, no, no.

05:01.644 --> 05:02.645
You're high.

05:03.212 --> 05:04.480
Duh, but...

05:04.480 --> 05:06.849
I think it'd be best if
I talked to you

05:06.849 --> 05:08.084
when you're sober.

05:08.084 --> 05:10.453
I don't know when that'll be,
Preston.

05:10.853 --> 05:13.122
I was kinda hopin' it'd be
by the morning.

05:13.122 --> 05:16.425
No, I'm busy,
I, I wake and bake then.

05:16.425 --> 05:17.760
That's a tough one.

05:17.760 --> 05:19.896
I wanna talk to you when
you have a clear mind.

05:20.596 --> 05:21.664
I don't...

05:21.664 --> 05:24.734
Again, good luck with finding
that day.

05:24.734 --> 05:25.902
[Preston] Danni...

05:25.902 --> 05:28.571
I'll, if it frees up,
I'll let you know, okay?

05:28.571 --> 05:31.073
-Danni...
-I'm, I'm gonna go take a bath.

05:31.073 --> 05:32.241
Okay, well if you're
takin' a bath,

05:32.241 --> 05:33.509
I'm takin' a bath.

05:33.509 --> 05:36.178
I don't...
It's, it's small in there...

05:36.178 --> 05:37.380
We've done that before.

05:37.380 --> 05:38.848
Think you could you lay down?

05:38.848 --> 05:39.882
In the small bed?

05:39.882 --> 05:41.984
Yeah.
Cool off.

05:41.984 --> 05:43.819
Okay, just, just sleep it off?

05:43.819 --> 05:45.221
Yeah.

05:45.221 --> 05:46.956
What's the difference?
Small bed, small bath.

05:46.956 --> 05:47.924
We've done both.

05:49.759 --> 05:50.860
Small couch.

05:51.894 --> 05:52.929
<i>Small apartment!</i>

05:59.168 --> 06:05.274
[phone ringing]

06:08.144 --> 06:09.278
-Hey.
-[Danni]<i> Hey.</i>

06:09.278 --> 06:10.313
[Sabrina]<i> What's up?</i>

06:10.313 --> 06:11.514
How are you?

06:13.015 --> 06:14.350
I'm worried about Maurice.

06:14.951 --> 06:17.453
I know.
Andi's gonna take care of it.

06:17.987 --> 06:18.921
I hope so.

06:18.921 --> 06:19.889
[Danni]<i> She will.</i>

06:20.323 --> 06:21.390
<i>But, um...</i>

06:21.390 --> 06:22.491
What is it?

06:22.491 --> 06:24.627
I have another problem.

06:24.961 --> 06:26.629
-[Sabrina]<i> What?
</i>-Yeah...

06:26.629 --> 06:29.298
Preston is asking me
to marry him.

06:30.633 --> 06:32.468
-What?!
-[Danni]<i> Yeah.</i>

06:32.468 --> 06:33.769
What did you say?!

06:33.769 --> 06:35.004
Hell no!

06:35.004 --> 06:36.072
[Sabrina]<i> Really?</i>

06:36.439 --> 06:38.975
I'm not ready to marry him.

06:39.241 --> 06:40.376
I get it.

06:40.376 --> 06:41.844
[Danni]<i> I'm not.</i>

06:42.845 --> 06:43.913
Well, what did he say?

06:43.913 --> 06:46.082
He wants to talk to me
when I'm sober.

06:46.082 --> 06:47.216
<i>Not smoking.</i>

06:47.216 --> 06:49.251
<i>What, what, what is that?</i>

06:49.251 --> 06:51.754
You know?
Have you met me not smoking?

06:51.754 --> 06:53.723
I don't know.
I don't know.

06:53.723 --> 06:55.558
Well, why don't you just talk
to the man?

06:55.558 --> 06:57.626
Okay, what's wrong with you?

06:57.626 --> 06:59.996
[music]

06:59.996 --> 07:00.930
Nothing.

07:01.297 --> 07:02.798
I'm gonna talk to you later.

07:03.232 --> 07:04.700
Panty man there?

07:04.700 --> 07:05.668
Bye, Danni.

07:05.668 --> 07:07.069
[Danni]<i> Tell him hey.</i>

07:12.842 --> 07:14.210
I'm smokin'.

07:14.210 --> 07:19.648
[music]

07:19.648 --> 07:20.950
Ooph!

07:20.950 --> 07:22.218
Ooh!

07:22.218 --> 07:23.819
You don't wanna go in there.

07:24.320 --> 07:26.122
'Cause I blew it up.

07:26.122 --> 07:27.256
[chuckling]

07:27.256 --> 07:28.557
Oh...

07:28.557 --> 07:30.092
I'm just kiddin'.

07:30.092 --> 07:32.528
I know, it's just kinda hard to
joke around with

07:32.528 --> 07:33.896
Maurice in jail.

07:35.131 --> 07:36.432
Damn.

07:36.432 --> 07:37.967
I know it is.

07:38.601 --> 07:39.835
You talk to Andi?

07:40.803 --> 07:41.971
Mm-hm.

07:41.971 --> 07:44.040
She said that she was gonna
try to help me.

07:44.473 --> 07:46.275
All right.
Good.

07:46.709 --> 07:48.110
Thanks for comin' by.

07:49.078 --> 07:50.413
I missed you.

07:51.781 --> 07:54.583
And thank you for
not being upset with Bayo.

07:56.352 --> 07:57.686
Yeah, it's cool.

07:59.789 --> 08:00.890
'Kay.

08:01.891 --> 08:02.825
Are you okay?

08:02.825 --> 08:06.395
Just...
Just really tired.

08:06.962 --> 08:08.330
I get it.

08:08.330 --> 08:10.666
Well, I can go,
I know you need your rest.

08:14.203 --> 08:15.538
Do you mind staying?

08:17.073 --> 08:18.307
Yeah, I'll stay.

08:18.307 --> 08:20.076
I also just...

08:20.076 --> 08:21.577
[Calvin] What?

08:25.214 --> 08:27.049
I can do whatever you want.

08:27.750 --> 08:28.551
Calvin...

08:28.551 --> 08:31.754
Okay, I'm sorry.
Go on.

08:32.354 --> 08:33.889
Can you just hold me?

08:34.824 --> 08:36.158
I can do that.

08:41.797 --> 08:43.132
[music]

08:43.132 --> 08:44.867
I'm just really scared.

08:45.367 --> 08:46.469
I know.

08:47.670 --> 08:49.071
This is so horrible.

08:49.672 --> 08:50.906
I know it is.

08:50.906 --> 08:54.410
[music]

08:54.410 --> 08:55.978
I just wanna feel safe.

08:55.978 --> 08:58.013
Hey.

08:58.013 --> 08:59.348
I got you.

08:59.348 --> 09:00.616
All right?

09:01.750 --> 09:03.452
I don't wanna lose my job.

09:03.452 --> 09:05.254
All right,
don't worry about that.

09:05.254 --> 09:06.689
You'll find another one.

09:07.123 --> 09:08.557
Not with the record.

09:09.058 --> 09:10.493
You didn't do anything.

09:11.660 --> 09:12.962
It doesn't matter.

09:14.763 --> 09:17.733
Plenty of people can't find
a job with a record.

09:17.733 --> 09:20.269
Okay, just relax.
Okay?

09:20.636 --> 09:23.239
What if Maurice gets weak and...

09:23.239 --> 09:25.908
decides to give me up for
something I didn't even do?

09:25.908 --> 09:27.977
Why would he--
You're overthinkin' this.

09:28.978 --> 09:30.212
I'm sorry.

09:30.212 --> 09:32.515
I've just never been through
anything like this.

09:33.482 --> 09:36.452
I know, but you just gotta take
things one step at a time.

09:36.452 --> 09:37.486
All right?

09:37.486 --> 09:41.390
[music]

09:41.390 --> 09:42.424
I don't think...

09:42.424 --> 09:44.493
anyone understands.

09:45.427 --> 09:46.862
My mom is sick.

09:48.264 --> 09:49.899
And I'm her sole supporter.

09:51.033 --> 09:52.401
Believe me...

09:52.401 --> 09:53.736
I understand.

09:54.803 --> 09:56.906
Yeah, you do.
I'm sorry.

09:58.240 --> 09:59.708
It's gonna be okay.

10:00.709 --> 10:02.811
-All right?
-You really think so?

10:03.979 --> 10:05.014
I do.

10:06.615 --> 10:08.651
Why'd he hook up with him?

10:10.186 --> 10:11.587
It's gonna be all right.

10:14.323 --> 10:15.558
I don't know.

10:16.492 --> 10:17.660
I hope so.

10:17.660 --> 10:20.162
It will, I promise you.
It will.

10:22.064 --> 10:23.566
Let's just go to bed.

10:24.500 --> 10:26.068
You need a good night's rest.

10:26.068 --> 10:28.637
I do, I couldn't even
sleep in there.

10:29.605 --> 10:30.873
I can imagine.

10:32.775 --> 10:34.710
I don't ever wanna go back.

10:37.913 --> 10:39.148
You won't.

10:39.148 --> 10:46.956
[music]

10:48.924 --> 10:51.160
It's gonna be all right.
All right?

10:51.160 --> 10:52.161
It's gonna be all right.

10:54.547 --> 10:58.017
[phone ringing]

10:58.551 --> 10:59.952
Hello?

10:59.952 --> 11:00.953
Bad time?

11:00.953 --> 11:01.988
[Andi]<i> No...</i>

11:01.988 --> 11:03.756
Looks like I'm gonna need
that number.

11:03.756 --> 11:05.224
Are you gonna call him?

11:06.659 --> 11:08.127
I don't really have a choice.

11:09.862 --> 11:10.830
Okay.

11:11.864 --> 11:13.766
I'll get the number for you
in the morning.

11:14.333 --> 11:15.601
Okay.

11:17.336 --> 11:20.173
Robin, I'm sorry.
About all this.

11:21.073 --> 11:22.108
Why are you sorry?

11:25.077 --> 11:25.945
Well...

11:25.945 --> 11:28.080
Hey, you gave me a head's up.

11:28.080 --> 11:29.282
I got it.

11:30.917 --> 11:32.885
-I know you do.
-[Robin]<i> Well...</i>

11:32.885 --> 11:34.220
until he comes and
breaks my arms

11:34.220 --> 11:35.288
'cause I don't pay him.

11:37.423 --> 11:38.891
You're gonna pay him.

11:38.891 --> 11:41.527
I'm gonna look at his fine print
and his terms, but, uh...

11:42.495 --> 11:43.896
I'm up against a wall.

11:45.164 --> 11:46.199
I'm really sorry.

11:46.832 --> 11:48.768
That Gary's a cunning one, huh?

11:50.236 --> 11:51.170
I know.

11:52.238 --> 11:53.272
You like that?

11:54.106 --> 11:56.776
I've never dealt with him
in business, so...

11:57.677 --> 11:59.178
Well, he's shrewd.

12:00.213 --> 12:01.180
I heard.

12:01.180 --> 12:02.748
And to make this move...

12:03.015 --> 12:04.250
[Andi]<i> Again.</i>

12:04.984 --> 12:06.919
But hey, you gave me
the head's up.

12:07.420 --> 12:08.688
I didn't.

12:08.688 --> 12:10.990
Well, you gave me
the information to help myself.

12:12.625 --> 12:13.759
I owe you one.

12:14.427 --> 12:15.795
You don't owe me anything.

12:15.795 --> 12:18.097
I was an asshole,
and I shouldn't have been.

12:18.631 --> 12:19.732
It's fine.

12:20.266 --> 12:22.301
Well, thank you for not
holding it against me.

12:22.301 --> 12:26.072
And thank you for helping me
with my friend.

12:26.872 --> 12:28.007
Sure.

12:28.274 --> 12:29.508
[Andi]<i> Um...</i>

12:29.508 --> 12:31.410
<i>I have another favor to ask.</i>

12:31.811 --> 12:33.145
I'm on my way.

12:33.646 --> 12:35.948
I did not mean it like that.

12:36.849 --> 12:39.218
Right, 'cause Gary's
probably on his way.

12:42.255 --> 12:43.623
Maurice Webb.

12:45.324 --> 12:46.626
Her accomplice?

12:47.360 --> 12:48.928
Don't do that.
He's innocent.

12:49.495 --> 12:51.897
Andi, are you sure you can
vouch for these people?

12:52.498 --> 12:53.432
Yeah.

12:53.799 --> 12:55.134
Absolutely.

12:56.569 --> 12:57.837
Okay, what do you need?

12:58.871 --> 13:02.475
Well, I was wondering
if you can...

13:02.475 --> 13:04.176
help me get bail for him?

13:05.144 --> 13:07.346
Andi, I do not have another
million dollars.

13:07.346 --> 13:08.881
You know my situation.

13:08.881 --> 13:10.216
[Andi]<i> I know that.</i>

13:10.216 --> 13:12.285
But could you at least...

13:12.285 --> 13:13.986
help me get in to see him?

13:15.521 --> 13:17.156
I'll give you a call
in the morning.

13:17.156 --> 13:18.157
[Andi]<i> Okay.</i>

13:18.858 --> 13:21.394
It's really cool to have
a powerful boss.

13:22.428 --> 13:23.362
Yeah?

13:24.597 --> 13:25.765
Thank you.

13:25.765 --> 13:27.667
Let's just hope
I stay your boss.

13:28.701 --> 13:31.070
You're gonna get through this.
Okay?

13:31.437 --> 13:32.772
Yeah, I hope so.

13:34.073 --> 13:35.474
All right, I'll see you
tomorrow.

13:35.875 --> 13:38.210
I'll see you then.
Bye.

13:38.644 --> 13:39.679
Bye.

13:46.819 --> 13:49.088
-Hi!
-[Gary] Hey.

13:49.088 --> 13:50.423
[door closing]

13:52.491 --> 13:54.093
Sorry, I thought
you were sleeping.

13:55.394 --> 13:57.997
No...
I was just on the phone.

13:58.664 --> 14:00.733
Yeah, I...

14:00.733 --> 14:02.068
I heard you.

14:05.471 --> 14:06.439
Who was that?

14:08.641 --> 14:10.343
We're not doin' that.

14:12.478 --> 14:13.713
I'm sorry.

14:13.713 --> 14:15.114
Okay.

14:17.650 --> 14:18.951
Were you...

14:18.951 --> 14:21.020
listening to my conversation?

14:22.421 --> 14:23.956
Yeah, I was.

14:26.392 --> 14:27.326
Why?

14:27.960 --> 14:30.429
Well, I came in and heard
voices at the door,

14:30.429 --> 14:33.265
so I thought you were in here
with someone.

14:34.767 --> 14:36.068
