All right.

27:39.802 --> 27:41.170
I will talk to you later.

27:41.170 --> 27:42.171
Sure.

27:42.171 --> 27:43.873
-[Fatima]<i> Bye.
</i>-Bye.

27:46.976 --> 27:49.846
-Your plant, I assume?
-Yes, mm-hm.

27:50.847 --> 27:53.650
So, I had my cousin hook him up
with someone that I knew

27:53.650 --> 27:55.251
he couldn't resist.

27:55.251 --> 27:57.687
When I tell you she is playin'
his ass like a fiddle,

27:57.687 --> 27:59.055
and he's fallin' for it.

27:59.589 --> 28:00.823
I love it!

28:01.591 --> 28:03.159
Oh, man.

28:04.560 --> 28:06.496
Don't you think this is
a little...

28:06.496 --> 28:07.864
elaborate?

28:07.864 --> 28:09.632
Andi, I know.
I know it's low.

28:09.632 --> 28:10.900
[Andi] Mm-hm.

28:10.900 --> 28:12.402
But look, I didn't know what
else to do

28:12.402 --> 28:13.569
besides have this -- popped.

28:13.569 --> 28:15.905
If "popped" means what
I think it means,

28:15.905 --> 28:18.741
then you absolutely cannot do
that option.

28:18.741 --> 28:20.777
It does mean that,
so that's why I'm doing this.

28:20.777 --> 28:24.847
Well, if you could please just
remind me to never get

28:24.847 --> 28:26.549
on your bad side,
that would be great.

28:26.549 --> 28:29.786
Reminded, yes.
But...

28:29.786 --> 28:32.455
What is all this talk about
takin' over the hedge fund?

28:32.455 --> 28:34.390
Is that your Gary?

28:34.390 --> 28:35.825
Scary Gary?

28:35.825 --> 28:38.328
He's not Scary Gary.
Anyway...

28:39.629 --> 28:41.030
Yeah, they are...

28:41.030 --> 28:43.499
Trying to make some major moves.

28:43.499 --> 28:45.268
But you can't say anything.

28:45.268 --> 28:46.869
I, I never do.
No.

28:46.869 --> 28:48.438
[Andi] They're trying to force
Robin out.

28:48.438 --> 28:52.909
And I just found out that Hayden
is very heavily involved.

28:53.509 --> 28:54.610
Which is...

28:54.610 --> 28:56.412
-Good to know.
-[Fatima] Hmm...

28:56.412 --> 28:57.981
Good to know what
I'm dealing with.

28:57.981 --> 28:59.015
Well...

28:59.015 --> 29:00.883
Do you think they'll
be able to do it?

29:02.151 --> 29:03.219
I don't know.

29:04.387 --> 29:06.122
So are you gonna tell Robin?

29:07.790 --> 29:09.125
He's a smart man.

29:09.959 --> 29:11.694
I think he'll figure it out.

29:12.295 --> 29:14.097
-Okay.
-[Andi] Well...

29:14.097 --> 29:16.766
I just have to say
that I don't...

29:16.766 --> 29:19.435
really like this thing
with your plant.

29:19.435 --> 29:20.737
That whole situation.

29:21.804 --> 29:23.272
Andi, I don't, either.
But...

29:24.474 --> 29:26.676
I get it.
I don't like it...

29:26.676 --> 29:28.244
But I get it.

29:28.244 --> 29:29.712
Good, I'm glad you get it.

29:29.712 --> 29:31.414
[Andi] Mm-hm...
Oh.

29:31.748 --> 29:33.616
Where is my...?
Oh, yes.

29:33.616 --> 29:35.351
Here.
Let me...

29:35.351 --> 29:36.986
Could've got this together
better for you.

29:36.986 --> 29:40.023
Could you take this file
for me, please?

29:40.023 --> 29:41.190
Thank you.

29:41.190 --> 29:42.392
Yes, I'm on it.

29:42.392 --> 29:43.760
Yes, I appreciate it.

29:43.760 --> 29:45.261
-[Fatima] Of course.
-All right, thank you.

29:45.261 --> 29:46.829
[Fatima] You're welcome.

29:51.367 --> 29:53.236
-[Calvin] Morning.
-Morning.

29:53.703 --> 29:54.837
[Calvin] I'mma get outta here.

29:54.837 --> 29:56.005
-Okay.
-[Calvin] All right.

29:56.005 --> 29:57.540
Thank you for bein' here.

29:57.540 --> 29:59.742
[Calvin] No problem.
[phone ringing]

29:59.742 --> 30:01.878
-Is that him?
-[Calvin] It's Maurice.

30:02.545 --> 30:03.579
Maurice?

30:03.880 --> 30:05.114
[Maurice]<i> Hello.</i>

30:05.715 --> 30:06.716
How are you?

30:06.716 --> 30:07.984
Oh, I'm wonderful.

30:07.984 --> 30:10.420
Gettin' ready to fly
to London tonight.

30:10.420 --> 30:11.554
[Calvin]<i> Maurice...</i>

30:11.554 --> 30:13.823
Stop askin' me that stupid shit!

30:13.823 --> 30:15.691
Look, I got you
on speakerphone,

30:15.691 --> 30:16.959
and Sabrina's here.

30:18.194 --> 30:19.295
Okay.

30:19.295 --> 30:20.396
Hi!

30:20.396 --> 30:21.397
Shit.

30:21.764 --> 30:22.932
[Sabrina]<i> What?</i>

30:22.932 --> 30:25.268
Y'all two still
bumpin' cats, huh?

30:26.069 --> 30:27.937
Will you stop it, Maurice?

30:28.271 --> 30:29.272
How are you?

30:29.939 --> 30:32.108
Oh, I'm pissed the -- off.
And yourself?

30:32.642 --> 30:33.709
I know.

30:33.709 --> 30:34.610
[Maurice]<i> [sighing]</i>

30:34.610 --> 30:35.778
<i>That damn Que.</i>

30:36.279 --> 30:37.346
I know, I know.

30:37.346 --> 30:38.314
Mm-hm.

30:39.182 --> 30:41.517
The prosecutor said that you
and Que were workin' together

30:41.517 --> 30:42.652
to get me in here.

30:42.652 --> 30:44.287
He's lying.

30:44.287 --> 30:46.956
-I know he is.
-[Sabrina]<i> Look, that was...</i>

30:46.956 --> 30:49.092
That has somethin' to do with
Andi, I don't know.

30:49.092 --> 30:50.259
She beat him in a divorce case,

30:50.259 --> 30:51.994
and now he's after her
or something.

30:51.994 --> 30:53.763
And that bitch is takin'
it out on me?!

30:53.763 --> 30:55.565
[Sabrina]<i> Yeah, I don't know
what's going on.</i>

30:56.399 --> 30:58.668
But I'm on my way to
Andi's office right now

30:58.668 --> 30:59.735
to figure it out.

30:59.735 --> 31:01.304
What the hell is she gonna do?!

31:01.304 --> 31:03.639
She got me out, maybe she can
help you, too.

31:03.639 --> 31:05.241
[Maurice]<i> Y'all better do
somethin'.</i>

31:05.241 --> 31:06.342
We are, I'm...

31:06.342 --> 31:08.077
Do you think you can call me
in an hour?

31:08.077 --> 31:09.045
[sighing]

31:09.045 --> 31:10.179
-[Maurice]<i> Yes.
</i>-[Sabrina] Okay.

31:10.179 --> 31:11.614
Well, I'm going to
her office now.

31:11.614 --> 31:12.648
Okay.

31:12.648 --> 31:13.883
Well, hurry up.

31:13.883 --> 31:15.384
I'm in here fightin'
for my virginity.

31:17.286 --> 31:18.287
We're on it.

31:18.888 --> 31:20.756
-Okay.
-[Sabrina]<i> I got you, I know.</i>

31:20.756 --> 31:22.425
Call me in one hour.

31:22.425 --> 31:23.759
I will.

31:24.427 --> 31:25.328
[Sabrina]<i> Okay.</i>

31:26.362 --> 31:27.497
Okay.

31:27.763 --> 31:29.165
Bye.

31:29.866 --> 31:31.067
All right, come on.

31:33.569 --> 31:34.504
Let me handle this.

31:35.304 --> 31:36.739
I wanna go with you.

31:37.740 --> 31:39.408
And I appreciate that.
But...

31:40.476 --> 31:41.544
I got this.

31:41.544 --> 31:44.147
All right, look.
I'mma go to work.

31:44.147 --> 31:45.815
But call me as soon as
you hear something.

31:45.815 --> 31:46.849
I will.

31:46.849 --> 31:48.151
-All right?
-Yeah.

31:48.684 --> 31:49.519
Thank you.

31:52.781 --> 31:54.149
[Danni] All right, ma'am.

31:54.149 --> 31:55.817
Thank you so much,
you'll be boarding shortly.

32:00.188 --> 32:02.090
Hey.

32:02.357 --> 32:03.425
How do you feel?

32:03.792 --> 32:05.060
What do you mean?

32:05.627 --> 32:07.329
I mean after all those drinks.

32:08.797 --> 32:10.966
Oh, you don't know.
You don't know.

32:10.966 --> 32:12.467
[Que] Know what?

32:12.467 --> 32:13.935
My liver's made of steel.

32:13.935 --> 32:16.071
Oh, yeah?
Me like.

32:17.539 --> 32:19.074
Should be askin' how you doin'.

32:19.074 --> 32:21.409
I'm good, baby girl.
I can handle mine.

32:21.409 --> 32:23.245
Good.
That's good.

32:24.045 --> 32:26.081
So, you wanna do it again?

32:26.081 --> 32:26.915
Hm?

32:26.915 --> 32:28.483
[Que] Grab dinner tonight.

32:28.483 --> 32:30.085
No, no, no.
Mm-mm.

32:30.085 --> 32:31.620
-Okay.
-[Danni] I do not.

32:31.620 --> 32:33.655
I was wondering if
I could come by.

32:33.655 --> 32:35.223
To your house.

32:35.857 --> 32:37.325
Excuse me?

32:37.325 --> 32:41.463
Well, maybe get some takeout,
have some drinks, smoke.

32:42.564 --> 32:45.267
Don't you have to be somewhere
by a certain time,

32:45.267 --> 32:47.102
that ankle bracelet on your leg?

32:47.102 --> 32:49.638
Yeah, but I'm working,
so as long as I'm here

32:49.638 --> 32:52.307
or there by a certain time,
it should all be good, you know?

32:53.141 --> 32:54.109
Mm-hm.

32:54.709 --> 32:55.544
What'd you do?

32:56.645 --> 32:57.879
What do you mean?

32:57.879 --> 32:59.214
You never told me what
you did to get

32:59.214 --> 33:01.016
that bracelet on your leg there.

33:04.986 --> 33:06.621
I got into a fight, and...

33:07.088 --> 33:08.890
I beat up this dude really bad

33:08.890 --> 33:10.525
for attacking somebody
that I love.

33:10.525 --> 33:12.827
Mm.
Yeah?

33:12.827 --> 33:14.229
[Que] Yeah.

33:14.229 --> 33:16.498
So, you went to jail for
a woman?

33:17.399 --> 33:18.533
Yeah.

33:19.534 --> 33:21.069
For my mama.

33:22.437 --> 33:24.206
Oh.
I see.

33:24.206 --> 33:25.207
Yeah.

33:26.007 --> 33:27.542
[knuckles cracking]

33:27.542 --> 33:28.877
And I'll do it again.

33:29.511 --> 33:30.579
I see.

33:32.547 --> 33:33.615
You don't believe me?

33:35.984 --> 33:38.320
You don't have social media.

33:38.920 --> 33:41.423
Oh.
You been lookin' me up.

33:41.423 --> 33:42.557
Mm-hm.

33:42.557 --> 33:44.859
And I cannot find anything
online about you.

33:44.859 --> 33:46.428
Damn, you been searchin' me?

33:46.428 --> 33:47.462
[Danni] Oh, yeah.

33:47.462 --> 33:49.297
I need to know why you
all up on me.

33:51.233 --> 33:53.368
Look, Danni.
I'm not into none of that.

33:54.236 --> 33:55.270
Mm-hm.

33:55.270 --> 33:56.538
I see that.

33:59.608 --> 34:01.042
I just wanna get to know you.

34:06.147 --> 34:07.916
Yeah, I got a situation, so...

34:07.916 --> 34:09.017
Yeah?

34:09.017 --> 34:10.218
[Danni] Mm-hm.

34:10.218 --> 34:11.753
That's cool,
we can just hang out.

34:11.753 --> 34:13.321
Drinkin', smokin'.

34:15.090 --> 34:16.258
Can I come over?

34:20.795 --> 34:21.930
No.

34:22.664 --> 34:24.199
I'm done with drama.

34:24.933 --> 34:26.334
I'm not into no drama.

34:27.002 --> 34:29.771
Something, I don't know what...

34:29.771 --> 34:32.173
Something tells me that you are.

34:33.208 --> 34:35.277
Just let me come over to
your house.

34:36.778 --> 34:38.546
-No.
-[Que] No?

34:38.546 --> 34:39.514
No.

34:40.582 --> 34:41.650
No.

34:42.450 --> 34:43.451
Okay, well...

34:48.523 --> 34:49.591
I need that.

34:51.192 --> 34:52.594
Text me your address.

34:54.162 --> 34:55.263
This is my number.

34:55.263 --> 34:57.032
I'll come over after work.

34:57.032 --> 34:58.667
Hello?
Can you hear?

34:58.667 --> 35:00.635
No.
You will not.

35:00.635 --> 35:01.970
See you then.

35:05.140 --> 35:07.108
Hello?
Joy?

35:07.509 --> 35:08.710
You're crazy!

35:09.144 --> 35:10.412
Just a little.

35:10.412 --> 35:12.514
-[Danni] You're crazy.
-Just a little.

35:12.514 --> 35:15.016
[door creaking]

35:17.552 --> 35:21.189
[music]

35:22.057 --> 35:23.958
Damn, Zac!

35:23.958 --> 35:24.959
Haha, you seen me.

35:24.959 --> 35:26.294
You look nice!

35:26.294 --> 35:28.263
Somethin' light.
Somethin' light.

35:28.263 --> 35:29.564
Karen!

35:29.564 --> 35:34.769
[music]

35:34.769 --> 35:36.037
What's up?

35:36.905 --> 35:38.039
Hi.

35:39.541 --> 35:40.775
I left you a message.

35:40.775 --> 35:42.043
Yeah, I got it.

35:43.578 --> 35:44.746
Okay.

35:45.080 --> 35:46.514
I text you back.

35:47.215 --> 35:48.483
I never got it.

35:53.388 --> 35:55.690
Shit, I forgot to press send.

35:57.392 --> 35:58.426
Yeah, okay.

35:59.961 --> 36:01.296
I did.

36:01.763 --> 36:02.697
Okay.

36:05.734 --> 36:06.768
You think I'm playin' your game?

36:07.402 --> 36:08.670
Excuse me?

36:08.670 --> 36:11.673
The one where you stay out
all hours of the night,

36:11.673 --> 36:13.808
and then pretend that you text
me to let me know?

36:13.808 --> 36:15.810
Can we just not do that today?

36:15.810 --> 36:16.745
[Karen] Okay.

36:17.312 --> 36:19.180
-All right.
-[Zac] Thank you.

36:19.180 --> 36:20.415
Just admit it, though.

36:21.883 --> 36:22.917
Okay.

36:22.917 --> 36:24.619
I was lyin' to you.

36:24.619 --> 36:25.987
Mm-hm.

36:25.987 --> 36:27.722
So let's just remember whose
habit that is.

36:29.090 --> 36:31.693
Right.
Hey, I got the documents.

36:32.527 --> 36:34.295
You wanted Andi to
look 'em over?

36:35.330 --> 36:37.465
Give me just a second.
Okay?

36:37.465 --> 36:38.733
Sorry.

36:38.733 --> 36:39.868
[Karen] Come on.

36:39.868 --> 36:41.302
[Zac] No, I just
got the documents.

36:41.302 --> 36:43.471
Just come on.
Okay?

36:44.272 --> 36:46.107
-[Zac] I really just wanna...
-Zac?!

36:46.107 --> 36:47.675
Come.

36:51.980 --> 36:53.047
[Pam] Hey!

36:53.047 --> 36:54.983
Don't be --
back there, Zac.

36:54.983 --> 36:56.851
[laughter]

36:56.851 --> 36:58.453
That's funny?
That's funny?

37:00.288 --> 37:01.923
[Karen] Zac, come on.

37:01.923 --> 37:03.258
It's not funny to me.

37:03.992 --> 37:05.059
[unintelligible]

37:05.059 --> 37:06.161
[door closing]

37:06.161 --> 37:07.395
[Karen] Let me see.

37:23.411 --> 37:25.880
Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Don't do that, don't do that!

37:25.880 --> 37:27.081
Do what?

37:27.081 --> 37:28.783
You gotta have Andi
look at that!

37:28.783 --> 37:29.818
[Karen] No, I don't.

37:30.485 --> 37:32.754
I'm, I can't,
I'm not takin' that, Karen.

37:32.754 --> 37:34.255
[Karen] Why not?

37:34.255 --> 37:36.257
You have to have your lawyer
look at that, at least.

37:36.257 --> 37:37.625
I don't need one.

37:38.560 --> 37:40.428
Look, Zac...

37:42.030 --> 37:43.698
Karen, I can't take that
like that.

37:43.698 --> 37:45.633
You have to have Andi
look at it, I'm sorry.

37:46.100 --> 37:47.602
You didn't even read it!

37:49.704 --> 37:50.738
[Karen] Okay.

37:51.105 --> 37:52.507
Thank you.

37:52.507 --> 37:55.510
[music]

37:55.510 --> 37:57.679
Them letters my mama
had me write,

37:57.679 --> 37:59.447
they was, they was good.

38:00.014 --> 38:01.783
I'm startin' to feel lighter.

38:01.783 --> 38:03.151
That's good.

38:03.685 --> 38:04.719
Yeah.

38:05.753 --> 38:07.822
Light enough to let
all this shit go.

38:08.690 --> 38:09.724
Wow, that's...

38:09.724 --> 38:11.125
That's real good.

38:11.125 --> 38:12.694
Mm-hm.

38:13.094 --> 38:14.362
You know what else?

38:15.663 --> 38:16.865
What's that?

38:17.866 --> 38:19.167
I'm gonna make the best of this.

38:19.667 --> 38:21.669
And you gonna make
the best of this.

38:22.103 --> 38:23.538
And we good.

38:25.006 --> 38:25.974
That's...

38:25.974 --> 38:27.675
That's the right attitude.

38:27.675 --> 38:28.743
Yes, it is.

38:29.110 --> 38:31.312
Thank you.
Seriously.

38:34.983 --> 38:36.217
Fatima's a cool chick.

38:36.217 --> 38:38.119
Whoa, whoa, now.

38:38.853 --> 38:41.856
I don't, I don't know what
you tryin' to do...

38:41.856 --> 38:43.458
Got goin' on, but...

38:44.926 --> 38:45.793
What?

38:46.594 --> 38:49.030
I, I mean, I know she
a cool chick and all, but...

38:49.797 --> 38:51.966
Letters don't make you change
overnight.

38:51.966 --> 38:53.835
No, they didn't.

38:53.835 --> 38:54.903
Right, so...

38:55.303 --> 38:57.138
We ain't gettin' any younger.

38:58.106 --> 39:00.775
There's no reason to keep
wastin' time on, you know...

39:00.775 --> 39:01.943
This.

39:02.944 --> 39:05.847
Right.

39:07.248 --> 39:08.550
Well...

39:09.884 --> 39:11.185
Thank you.

39:13.021 --> 39:14.389
Congratulations.

39:15.757 --> 39:17.158
For?

39:17.158 --> 39:19.260
For your engagement.

39:19.260 --> 39:21.729
And fatherhood.

39:21.729 --> 39:22.964
Thank you.

39:24.532 --> 39:26.768
Well, I have a client I gotta
get back to,

39:26.768 --> 39:27.835
so we should head out.

39:29.003 --> 39:29.971
Of course.

39:30.605 --> 39:37.211
[music]

39:37.211 --> 39:39.314
Ain't nobody doing nothin'
in there.

39:42.050 --> 39:43.585
I'll see you later, Karen.

39:43.585 --> 39:44.752
Okay.

39:45.053 --> 39:46.521
Hey!

39:48.723 --> 39:50.024
What?

39:50.024 --> 40:02.003
[music]

40:02.437 --> 40:03.905
Sorry about that.

40:03.905 --> 40:08.309
[music]

40:08.309 --> 40:09.410
[Zac] Later, Pam.

40:09.410 --> 40:11.913
Fatima gon' kick yo ass.

40:11.913 --> 40:13.348
Shut up, Pam.

40:13.348 --> 40:19.354
[music]

40:19.354 --> 40:21.322
So, damn!

40:21.322 --> 40:22.523
[Karen] What?

40:22.523 --> 40:24.158
So y'all gettin' along
like that?

40:24.659 --> 40:26.828
It's all good, Pam.
It really is.

40:26.828 --> 40:28.196
You're sure?

40:28.196 --> 40:29.397
What'd I say?

40:30.064 --> 40:32.166
All right, 'cause if you was in
there more than five minutes,

40:32.166 --> 40:33.735
I was comin' in after you.

40:34.235 --> 40:35.670
For what?

40:35.670 --> 40:38.006
You know what happened
the last time he was back there.

40:40.441 --> 40:41.809
Pam, go do some work.

40:41.809 --> 40:43.411
-Okay?
-That's what I'm doing.

40:43.411 --> 40:45.246
Do it over there.

40:45.246 --> 40:50.018
[music]

40:50.852 --> 40:52.053
[Fatima] Hey, girl.

40:52.053 --> 40:53.988
-Hey.
-What's goin' on?

40:57.425 --> 40:59.394
You and Zac...

41:00.094 --> 41:01.329
You're good, right?

41:01.329 --> 41:03.031
Y'all are still together?

41:03.031 --> 41:04.866
Yeah, we good.

41:05.333 --> 41:06.634
Okay.

41:07.535 --> 41:09.504
